:MCI COMMONNICATIONS Corp, dem say e don file one shelf registration wit di Securities and Exchange Commission to issue as much as $750 million debt securities.

Di debt na on top Merrill Lynch Capital Market, Drexel Burnham Inc, Goldman, Sachs & Co, and Salomon Brothers Inc.

Di money wey be sey de go refinish di one wey Washington, D.C.E., de go refinish di low interest rate, and oder general purpose.

Di date wey dey for di registration go dey determined by di SEC.

